The Details
Origin
Handcrafted in Florence, Italy from the finest Italian
top-grain leather in the same factory that makes
for Gucci and other leading brands
Features
Adjustable and removable leather strap
Heavy canvas lining and inner zip pocket for an iPhone and other valuables
Hardware
Gold zipper closure
Dimensions
The Crossbody Bag is made from the finest Italian
pebbled leather in just the right proportions. The
perfect minimal design for everyday wear, featuring
a safe space for your phone and carry-on
essentials. It is the ideal bag for transitioning from
day to night, breakfast to dinner, with an infinite
versatile appeal and timeless durability. The hard
part will be deciding which finish to choose from.
